What you need to know:

Kimathi said after roping in KCB Bank as their financial partners, the event that is funded jointly by public private partners, will see more companies coming on board next week.“We can’t quantify the actual cost of the event because we are learning since everything is new for us with the event making a return to the WRC vanguard, “said Kimathi, adding that lot of the investment will be utilised over the years.